		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you mean $78, that's SEI, the first instruction in 99.9% of all 6502 programs, so yeah, it's valid. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
