		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think I just now understood what the opcode matrix on the wiki means. I found another table that just lists values and their opcodes, and I realize that the table columns are just offsets from the rows, and the opcode is the row+column added together. Sorry, this is my first time doing emulation of this scale so I'm learning as I go along.

		

